  "time_ut": 1657715132,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0da2\u0db1\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc1\u0dc0\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A request from General Shavendra to the young people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chief of Defense Staff General Shavendra Silva said that the people of the country, especially the youth, are requested to support the armed forces and the police to maintain law and order in the country until the next President is appointed.",
        "\"The three armed forces and the police have acted according to the existing constitution. The Speaker told us that the resignation of the President will take place today.",
        "With the resignation of the President, we discussed with him the measures to be taken until the appointment of the next President.",
        "The three armed forces and the Inspector General of Police asked the Speaker to hold a party leadership meeting and inform us of the measures to be taken until the next President is appointed.",
        "Its decisions are to be announced to the people. We especially request the young people to announce this situation and support the armed forces and the police to maintain peace in the country until the next President is appointed.",
        "Support the armed forces and police to maintain law and order while protecting government and private property.\""
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "Shavendra",
          "label": "PERSON"
        }
      ],
